'''貝靈漢姆'''（'''Bellingham'''，{{IPAc-en|ˈ|b|ɛ|l|ɪ|n|dʒ|əm}}<ref>{{USdict|bĕl′·ĭn·jəm}}</ref>）是一個位於[[英國|英國]][[諾森伯蘭郡|諾森伯蘭郡]]的[[村莊|村莊]]，在[[紐卡斯爾|紐卡斯爾]]西北，[[泰恩河|北泰恩河]]流經。附近有Hareshaw Linn瀑布。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://hareshawlinn.com/ |title=Hareshaw Linn |access-date=2013-12-09 |archive-date=2021-01-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210123102756/http://www.hareshawlinn.com/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

此地因是[[平寧步道|平寧步道]]的終點而知名，因此遊客較多。當地報名為“Hexham Courant”，有一個建於1893年的高爾夫球場。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bellinghamgolfclub.com/ |title=Bellingham Golf Club |access-date=2013-12-09 |archive-date=2021-02-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211121050/http://www.bellinghamgolfclub.com/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

遺產中心（Heritage Centre）是當地博物館，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bellingham-heritage.org.uk/ |title=Bellingham Heritage Centre |access-date=2013-12-09 |archive-date=2021-05-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210506180258/https://bellingham-heritage.org.uk/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 保存了許多當地家族的族譜和老照片。

因為有獨特的[[桶形穹窿|桶形穹窿]]，當地建於13世紀，於17世紀重建的聖卡斯伯特教堂（St Cuthbert's Church）成爲了國家一級保護建築。<ref>Tomlinson, W W, 1888. Comprehensive Guide to Northumberland</ref> 村子中還有一個足球隊。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.football.mitoo.co.uk/LeagueTab.cfm?TblName=Matches&DivisionID=6741&LeagueCode=TAL2009 |title=Tyneside Amateur League Division One: League Table |access-date=2013-12-09 |archive-date=2012-03-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120314031858/http://www.football.mitoo.co.uk/LeagueTab.cfm?TblName=Matches&DivisionID=6741&LeagueCode=TAL2009 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

